data.description:
Welcome to your Tropical Retreat! This stunning 4-bedroom single-family residence is nestled in the heart of W Boca in Boca Vista Estates offering an enviable lifestyle. With low HOA fees, this gem sits on an oversized lot, providing ample space for outdoor activities and endless possibilities. You'll be greeted by a convenient 3-car garage. Step inside + discover a wide open floor plan w/ patio doors walking out to a newly resurfaced saltwater pool, perfect for relaxing + entertaining. Adjacent to the pool, a hot tub awaits to melt away your worries after a long day.Meticulous care has been given to this home with recent upgrades including a new roof, tile flooring, and a whole house generator.Possible room for expansion.Community pool, tennis and other recreational amenities The private backyard oasis is surrounded by lush landscaping and boasts beautiful fruit trees, creating a serene and tropical atmosphere. Feel secure during storm season with the included accordion hurricane shutters, offering peace of mind and protection for your loved ones.

As an added bonus, this home features a whole-house generator, guaranteeing uninterrupted power supply during any unforeseen circumstances. The possibilities are truly endless in this exceptional property.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Schedule a showing today and prepare to be captivated by all that this residence has to offer. Your dream lifestyle awaits!
